@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000

### ========================================
### 1. GENERAL & HEALTH CHECKS
### ========================================

### Root Welcome Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### API Documentation List
GET {{baseUrl}}/api

###

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### ========================================
### 2. AUTHENTICATION (JWT & COOKIES)
### ========================================

### Generate JWT Token (Admin Login)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/jwt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@medicare.com",
  "role": "Admin"
}

###

### Generate JWT Token (Doctor Login)
# @name loginDoctor
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/jwt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sarah.jenkins@medicare.com",
  "role": "Doctor"
}

###

### Generate JWT Token (Patient Login)
# @name loginPatient
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/jwt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "alice.smith@example.com",
  "role": "Patient"
}

###

### Logout (Clears HTTP-only cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout

### ========================================
### 3. ROLE AUTHORIZATION TESTS
### ========================================
# Note: You must run the respective login request above to set the cookie first

### Test Admin Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin-test

###

### Test Doctor Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/doctor-test

###

### Test Patient Access
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/patient-test


### ========================================
### 4. USERS API
### ========================================

### Register a New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Smith",
  "email": "alice.smith@example.com",
  "role": "Patient",
  "photoURL": "https://example.com/photos/alice.jpg",
  "bloodGroup": "O+",
  "createdAt": "2026-06-29T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users

###

### Get a Single User by Email
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/alice.smith@example.com

###

### Update User Role
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/alice.smith@example.com/role
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "Admin"
}
